<div class="intro">
<div class="welcome">
Welcome to ECS, the School  of Electronics and Computer Science at the University of Southampton. ECS is one of the world's leading centres for 
<a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050710083458/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/research/">research</a>, 
<a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050710083458/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/about/teaching/">teaching</a>, <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050710083458/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/business/">enterprise and innovation</a> in Electronics, Electrical Engineering and Computer Science.
<div class="sig">Head of School: <a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050710083458/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/people/wh">Professor Wendy Hall</a></div>
</div>
<div class="headline"><a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050710083458/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/757"><img src="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050710083458im_/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/image.php?id=news_757_img&amp;maxw=200&amp;maxh=150&amp;corners=10&amp;edge=1&amp;checksum=e062099412b611eee25b3280d0a70b02&amp;fn=fn.png" alt="Huda El Mubarek" title="Huda El Mubarek (Copyright: Steve Shrimpton)" border="0" width="99" height="150" class="thumbnail" /></a><h2 class="hide">Headline News</h2><h3><a href="http://ia360911.us.archive.org:9090/wayback/20050710083458/http://www.ecs.soton.ac.uk/news/757">ECS researcher awarded prestigious Research Fellowship</a></h3><p>An ECS researcher whose PhD results have already been patented by the University has been awarded a prestigious five-year research fellowship. Dr Huda Abdel Wahab Abdel Rahim El Mubarek of the School of Electronics and Computer Science (ECS) at the University of Southampton has been awarded a prestigious five-year research fellowship by the Royal Academy of Engineering (RAEng) jointly with the Engineering and Physical Sciences Research Council (EPSRC). This is the first time that this award has been made to a female member of the University.</p><p></p></div></div><div class='rightside'>

